column2: hey almond list wall street journal articles with update times equal to this year
column3: now => ( @com.wsj.get ) filter param:updated:Date == start_of unit:year => notify

column2: their link of my instagram pictures
alert me wherever new york times clauses published this week change and the update time is earlier than DURATION_0 after last year with the text in real life
column3: monitor ( ( @com.nytimes.get_front_page ) filter param:updated:Date >= start_of unit:week and param:updated:Date <= end_of unit:year + DURATION_0 ) => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.say param:message:String = " in real life "

column2: find my dropbox files in alphabetical order having bigger size than NUMBER_0 byte
column3: now => ( @com.dropbox.list_folder param:order_by:Enum(modified_time_decreasing,modified_time_increasing,name_decreasing,name_increasing) = enum:name_increasing ) filter param:file_size:Measure(byte) >= NUMBER_0 unit:byte => notify

column2: when it stops snowing in LOCATION_0 tell me my google drive files smaller than NUMBER_0 gigabytes
column3: ( edge ( monitor ( @org.thingpedia.weather.current param:location:Location = LOCATION_0 ) ) on not param:status:Enum(raining,cloudy,sunny,snowy,sleety,drizzling,windy) == enum:snowy ) => ( ( @com.google.drive.list_drive_files ) filter param:file_size:Measure(byte) <= NUMBER_0 unit:GB ) => notify

column2: number the list of all memes with name equivalent to pepperidge farm remembers
column3: now => ( @com.imgflip.list ) filter param:name:String == " pepperidge farm remembers " => notify

column2: i want a photo positioned on facebook
hey almond what are a price estimate for uber from here to LOCATION_0 having high estimates lower than CURRENCY_0 ?
column3: now => ( @com.uber.price_estimate param:end:Location = LOCATION_0 param:start:Location = location:current_location ) filter param:high_estimate:Currency <= CURRENCY_0 => notify

column2: give me posts in the washington post capital weather gang blog when somebody sends me a direct message
if the corporation name is lemaitre vascular inc. let me know of updates in novadaq technologies inc stocks
column3: edge ( monitor ( @com.yahoo.finance.get_stock_quote param:stock_id:Entity(tt:stock_id) = " novadaq technologies inc " ^^tt:stock_id ) ) on param:company_name:String == " lemaitre vascular inc. " => notify

column2: auto share my new dropbox files that changed most recently on linkedin
show the message real time in case of changes in articles in the washington post in section business with headlines equal to okcupid attack mozilla over gay rights
column3: monitor ( ( @com.washingtonpost.get_article param:section:Enum(politics,opinions,local,sports,national,world,business,lifestyle) = enum:business ) filter param:title:String == " okcupid attack mozilla over gay rights " ) => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.say param:message:String = " real time "

column2: make a blog post with their titles of canals i am subscribed to on youtube as the title on tumblr
give me NUMBER_0 many videos matching their industry of my linkedin profile on youtube
column3: now => ( @com.linkedin.get_profile ) join ( @com.youtube.search_videos param:count:Number = NUMBER_0 ) on param:query:String = param:industry:String => notify
